Greatest Common Divisor of Fibonacci Numbers

\begin{array}{c}\n\operatorname{gcd}\left(\left(f_{m}\right) f_{n}\right)=f_{9 c d(m, n)} \\\nf_{k}=f_{k-1}+f_{k-2}\n\end{array}[imath]\operatorname{gcd}\left(\left(f_{m}\right) f_{n}\right)=f_{9 c d(m, n)} [/imath] [imath]f_{k}=f_{k-1}+f_{k-2}[/imath]
